        "text": "Kelly was so great to work with for my pictures. She has a good setup in her studio, made me feel comfortable and did a great job of getting me into good looking poses. And the best part - my pics came out GREAT! I'd definitely recommend Kelly."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-04",
        "text": "Kelly was great to work with! She did an excellent job with my team's professional headshots and was excellent at coordinating and working with our group even when two team members had to be rescheduled. I would recommend Kelly for any business that wants to get their team cohesive professional headshots for website, social media, or personal use."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2026-04",
        "text": "Kelly Miranda Photography stands out as one of the most inviting and professional photography businesses in Durango, Colorado. Her website beautifully showcases family photography, newborn photography, maternity portraits, weddings, and headshots, and her style feels natural, emotional, and timeless. You can tell she truly cares about families and about creating artwork people will treasure for years. Even though I haven’t booked with her yet, I’m genuinely impressed by the warmth of her brand and the quality of her work. If you’re searching for a Durango photographer who feels both talented and personal, Kelly Miranda Photography absolutely deserves your attention."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2024-06",
        "text": "Kelly did an outstanding job recently at my son's wedding in New Jersey. Not being familiar with the hotel or venue,  she arrived early to scope out the best places to take pictures. The pictures at the venue are so beautiful! She captured the day perfectly! She took every picture we asked and more. She was very professional but made sure everyone was comfortable and enjoying the event. She is a very talented photographer and I highly recommend her."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-01",
        "text": "If you're looking for a Durango family photographer, Kelly is incredible! We were wanting to do the \"awkward JCPenney studio  family portrait\" trend, and her photos turned out even better than we could have hoped! I was so scared a photographer wouldn't take on such an unserious shoot, but she openly accepted, embraced, and made our concept even better. Our friends came in from all over the country over the holidays. It was so easy to schedule a time with her.\n\nWe had very little time to prepare poses or looks we were going for, and I was so surprised to see Kelly had made an entire gallery of formations and looks for us to recreate. The time in her studio was so efficient, yet flexible. Everyone felt comfortable requesting specific groupings and ideas. She made this shoot an entire experience we won't ever forget."
      }
